  ISO Standards (Registered via SWIFT, SIX, ISO)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  ISO 3166-1 Country Codes
    Copyright International Organization for Standardization (ISO).
    Country-code seed data is fetched from the ISO publication at runtime by
    the reference-data ingestion pipeline (see ref-data-pipelines/ingestion/
    dlt_ref_iso_codes.py). No ISO-published CSV is redistributed within this
    repository.

  ISO 4217 Currency Codes
    Copyright International Organization for Standardization (ISO).
    Currency-code seed data is fetched from the SIX Group publication at
    runtime. No ISO-published list is redistributed.

  ISO 10383 Market Identifier Codes (MIC)
    Copyright International Organization for Standardization (ISO); published
    by SWIFT. MIC seed data is fetched from the ISO20022 registry at runtime.

  ISO 10962 Classification of Financial Instruments (CFI)
    Copyright International Organization for Standardization (ISO).
    CFI category mappings are referenced in the instrument model.

  ISO 17442 Legal Entity Identifier (LEI)
    Copyright International Organization for Standardization (ISO).
    LEI format validation is implemented in the party model; LEIs are
    resolved at runtime via the GLEIF concatenated file.

  ISO 20275 Entity Legal Form (ELF) Code List
    Copyright International Organization for Standardization (ISO).
    ELF code seed data is fetched at runtime.


